"30:24:7" : {s: 30, a: 24, w: 7, r: "نزل", t: "وَيُنَزِّلُ", l: "نَزَّلَ", lc: 62, tl: "wayunazzilu", lb: "ধাপে ধাপে অবতীর্ণ করা, ধাপে ধাপে প্রকাশ করা ",e: "and He sends down", b: "বর্ষণ করেছিলেন", f: 5, rm: "to descend, come down, go down, happen, alight at, settle in a place, lodge. anzala - to send down, give. nazulun - that which is prepared for a guests entertainment, abode, gift. manzil - mansion, station. nazzala - to cause to descend, send down. tanziil - sending down, divine revelation, orderly arrangement and authentic compilation, gradual revelation."},
